    tonum←{0∊⍴⍵:⍬ ⋄ w←⍕⍵ ⋄ ((w='-')/w)←'¯' ⋄ ⊃(//)⎕VFI w}

    fmtNum←{⍺←⊢ ⋄ w←⍺⍕⍵ ⋄ (('¯'=,w)/,w)←'-' ⋄ w}

    ∇ r←{d}commaFmt n
